---
title: Pickled Red Onions
source: https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cz7G8ORyGrl/
tags: condiment
---

Finely slice @red onion{1} and place in a jar. Add @salt{1%tsp} and @sugar{1%tbsp}. Add @apple cider vinegar{4%tbsp} then fill the rest of the jar with boiling water. Best the next day but great even after just a few hours.
